What is the projected market size & growth rate of the Mainframe Security Market?

Market Analysis and Size

As the mainframe environment has thousands of customers instantaneously performing extensive range of application with changing performance profiles, multi-layered security is needed to protect the mainframe. Mainframe safety helps the agency to hit upon threats, decrease cost and observer coverage and regulations. It additionally enables in reducing the enterprise hazard through implementing safety coverage and providing risk remediation, near loop and automatic safety intelligence.

